\section{Concluding remarks}

It looks as though the MDS+DS approach can be used for microarray data and that this gives results not dissimilar to the lasso. Given how long the lasso has been in development, it is very encouraging that results from MDS+DS are rather close. Perhaps given further development the approach can begin to rival that of the lasso for applications where distance between observations rather than the actual value matters. 
 
